Config.Description:
Start time for the TitleCardMaker's scheduled operation&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

Container Variable: &lt;b&gt;TCM_RUNTIME&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Command Line Argument: &lt;b&gt;--runtime&lt;/b&gt;

How often to run the TitleCardMaker&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

Container Variable: &lt;b&gt;TCM_FREQUENCY&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Command Line Argument: &lt;b&gt;--frequency&lt;/b&gt;

Container filepath of the global preference file&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Container Variable: &lt;b&gt;TCM_PREFERENCES&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Command Line Argument: &lt;b&gt;--preferences&lt;/b&gt;

Container filepath to write all missing assets to&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

Container Variable: &lt;b&gt;TCM_MISSING&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Command Line Argument: &lt;b&gt;--missing&lt;/b&gt;

Verbosity of output log&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

Container Variable: &lt;b&gt;TCM_LOG&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Command Line Argument: &lt;b&gt;--log&lt;/b&gt;

File to monitor for Tautulli integration&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

Container Variable: &lt;b&gt;TCM_TAUTULLI_UPDATE_LIST&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Command Line Argument: &lt;b&gt;--tautulli-update-list&lt;/b&gt;

How often to check for the Tautulli update file&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

Container Variable: &lt;b&gt;TCM_TAUTULLI_UPDATE_FREQUENCY&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Command Line Argument: &lt;b&gt;--tautulli-update-frequency&lt;/b&gt;
